00:18:44,150 --> 00:18:48,600
I will keep Mingyuan in mind.

266
00:18:48,600 --> 00:18:50,960
I just wanted to pay you a visit.

267
00:18:50,960 --> 00:18:55,610
There will be more work in the future.

268
00:18:55,610 --> 00:19:00,750
That's nothing. If I can get more young people to see and like them,

269
00:19:00,750 --> 00:19:03,880
it's what's meaningful.

270
00:19:03,880 --> 00:19:06,350
The patterns Director Xia sent over

271
00:19:06,350 --> 00:19:08,620
are done and ready.

272
00:19:08,620 --> 00:19:10,930
Since you are here, you can check them out.

273
00:19:10,930 --> 00:19:12,570
Okay.

274
00:19:15,840 --> 00:19:18,180
