00:27:59,280 --> 00:28:00,750
Nothing.

388
00:28:01,220 --> 00:28:02,960
Let's eat.

389
00:28:03,690 --> 00:28:05,810
What took you so long?

390
00:28:05,810 --> 00:28:09,290
I need to do makeup.

391
00:28:14,180 --> 00:28:15,930
Let's eat.

392
00:28:17,060 --> 00:28:19,220
What have you planned for today?

393
00:28:19,220 --> 00:28:22,690
You know Suzhou well.

394
00:28:22,690 --> 00:28:25,360
Do you have any good suggestions?

395
00:28:32,110 --> 00:28:33,690
Hello.

396
00:28:43,770 --> 00:28:45,960
When did it happen?

397
00:28:47,610 --> 00:28:49,180
Okay.

398
00:28:50,090 --> 00:28:52,150
I'm heading back now.

399
00:28:58,260 --> 00:29:01,670
What is it? Did something happen?

400
00:29:06,690 --> 00:29:09,170
It's an emergency.

401
00:29:09,800 --> 00:29:11,800
I have to be back to Shanghai now.

402
00:29:15,990 --> 00:29:19,130
What are you doing here? They are saving her inside. What are you doing?

403
00:29:19,130 --> 00:29:20,290
How is Qian Qian right now?

404
00:29:20,290 --> 00:29:21,730
They are saving her. Can't you see?

405
00:29:21,730 --> 00:29:24,580
- I'm asking you how is she right now!
- Don't agitate yourself.

406
00:29:27,770 --> 00:29:28,920
How long has she been there?

407
00:29:28,920 --> 00:29:31,060
She just got in.

408
00:29:32,220 --> 00:29:35,400
Let's wait here.

409
00:29:35,870 --> 00:29:39,680
- No. No. I can't. Wait here.
- Okay.

410
00:29:39,680 --> 00:29:41,750
I need to wait for Tang Mingxuan to get here.

411
00:29:41,750 --> 00:29:44,300
I just called him. He said he will be coming right now.

412
00:29:44,300 --> 00:29:46,900
Why did you call him here?

413
00:29:46,900 --> 00:29:51,260
What do you know? Do you know Qian Qian better or do I?

414
00:29:51,260 --> 00:29:52,930
She doesn't want to see you or me.

415
00:29:52,930 --> 00:29:55,650
She wants to see Tang Mingxuan the most.

416
00:29:55,650 --> 00:29:57,820
Have you thought about us?

417
00:29:57,820 --> 00:30:01,860
What are you calling Tang Mingxuan here for? To hurt her for the second time?

418
00:30:01,860 --> 00:30:04,780
- Are you?
- What do you know?

419
00:30:06,050 --> 00:30:08,330
How is she doing?

420
00:30:08,330 --> 00:30:10,390
She is out of the danger zone,

421
00:30:10,390 --> 00:30:13,220
but she is worse than we predicted.

422
00:30:13,220 --> 00:30:15,170
What does that mean?

423
00:30:15,170 --> 00:30:17,300
Fang Qian's condition got worse.

424
00:30:17,300 --> 00:30:20,750
Also, it's evolving very rapidly.

425
00:30:20,750 --> 00:30:24,160
What we did today is just to keep her stable for a while.

426
00:30:25,050 --> 00:30:28,200
- Temporarily...
Is there anything else to be done?

427
00:30:28,200 --> 00:30:31,630
Stabilizing her is the best we can do today.

428
00:30:35,830 --> 00:30:37,430
- It can't be...
- It can't be...

429
00:30:37,430 --> 00:30:41,600
She is so young.

430
00:30:41,600 --> 00:30:43,590
I...

431
00:30:43,590 --> 00:30:46,780
I will find the best doctor in Europe

432
00:30:46,780 --> 00:30:50,640
to have consultation with you, is that okay?

433
00:31:05,060 --> 00:31:07,820
Do you like me, Mingxuan?

434
00:31:09,090 --> 00:31:11,430
Do you like me a little bit?

435
00:31:16,200 --> 00:31:18,130
Are you kidding?

436
00:31:21,220 --> 00:31:24,790
What are you thinking about all the time?

437
00:31:27,350 --> 00:31:29,090
What?

438
00:31:29,090 --> 00:31:31,310
Not even a little bit?

439
00:31:36,190 --> 00:31:38,920
If you say a little bit,

440
00:31:40,330 --> 00:31:43,220
then it has to be between brother and sister.

441
00:31:59,340 --> 00:32:01,710
I'm going to the restroom.

442
00:32:42,890 --> 00:32:46,340
The patient is asleep. Don't get her excited when she wakes up.

443
00:32:46,340 --> 00:32:47,890
Got it.

444
00:32:48,390 --> 00:32:49,960
Thank you.

445
00:32:54,350 --> 00:32:56,040
Uncle Fang.

446
00:32:56,040 --> 00:32:59,860
What are you doing here? I don't want to see you. Leave.

447
00:32:59,860 --> 00:33:01,200
I want to see Qian Qian.

448
00:33:01,200 --> 00:33:04,330
It's within the Fang family. It has nothing to do with you. Leave now.

449
00:33:04,330 --> 00:33:06,320
Stop it.

450
00:33:08,180 --> 00:33:12,130
Tang Mingxuan, I'm letting you in.

451
00:33:12,630 --> 00:33:15,280
But Qian Qian's life is holding on by a thread.

452
00:33:15,280 --> 00:33:18,670
I hope you know what to talk about and what to do

453
00:33:18,670 --> 00:33:20,370
once you enter.

454
00:33:23,460 --> 00:33:25,070
Got it.

455
00:33:27,690 --> 00:33:29,330
We can't let him...

456
00:33:29,330 --> 00:33:33,150
Enough. That's enough!

457
00:34:43,190 --> 00:34:45,330
Mingxuan.

458
00:34:59,170 --> 00:35:01,540
Don't say anything.

459
00:35:07,880 --> 00:35:10,730
I will be here.

460
00:35:12,330 --> 00:35:14,570
Just rest here.

461
00:35:43,860 --> 00:35:45,850
It smells so good.

462
00:35:45,850 --> 00:35:49,240
You are back. Wash your hands and eat.

463
00:35:49,240 --> 00:35:51,230
Mom, what did you make?

464
00:35:51,230 --> 00:35:53,370
Guess.

465
00:35:53,370 --> 00:35:55,070
Your favorite braised winter melon.

466
00:35:55,070 --> 00:35:56,350
Mom, you're great.

467
00:35:56,350 --> 00:35:58,580
Mo Fan said he is not coming back tonight.

468
00:35:58,580 --> 00:36:00,040
It's just us two.

469
00:36:00,040 --> 00:36:01,280
There's soup.

470
00:36:01,280 --> 00:36:03,260
Remember to wash your hands.

471
00:36:21,020 --> 00:36:23,780
[Tang Mingxuan]

472
00:36:26,430 --> 00:36:29,180
The number you called is not available.

473
00:36:29,180 --> 00:36:33,130
