480
00:37:12,070 --> 00:37:14,260
Did you fight?

481
00:37:14,260 --> 00:37:16,530
No, no, no.

482
00:37:16,530 --> 00:37:20,910
So he is busy. He will call you back when he is not.

483
00:37:20,910 --> 00:37:23,240
He must be busy.

484
00:37:24,820 --> 00:37:27,120
When are you thinking of

485
00:37:27,120 --> 00:37:30,180
bringing him home to see me?

486
00:37:31,370 --> 00:37:35,800
I will ask him. He is a busy guy.

487
00:37:35,800 --> 00:37:38,320
Mom, eat. The food is getting cold.

488
00:37:38,320 --> 00:37:40,590
Have some more.

489
00:37:40,590 --> 00:37:44,130
You are best at changing topics.

490
00:37:44,130 --> 00:37:47,950
Since he is so busy, what does he do?

491
00:37:47,950 --> 00:37:51,200
Mom, don't be like other parents,

492
00:37:51,200 --> 00:37:53,910
asking about his job, siblings,

493
00:37:53,910 --> 00:37:57,250
parents, and background.

494
00:37:58,540 --> 00:38:00,650
You can never keep a daughter around you.

495
00:38:00,650 --> 00:38:05,150
I just asked you one question and you react like this.

496
00:38:05,150 --> 00:38:08,050
All right. I will have to believe that

497
00:38:08,050 --> 00:38:10,440
he is an outstanding young man.

498
00:38:11,070 --> 00:38:13,700
You trust me so much?

499
00:38:13,700 --> 00:38:16,020
Because you are outstanding.

500
00:38:17,650 --> 00:38:20,180
She wouldn't want someone who has no goals,

501
00:38:20,180 --> 00:38:22,760
no dreams and no ambitions.

502
00:38:24,210 --> 00:38:28,120
However, for guys like them,

503
00:38:28,120 --> 00:38:30,860
love is not the only thing in their lives.

504
00:38:31,770 --> 00:38:33,700
In his life,

505
00:38:33,700 --> 00:38:37,130
there's always something more important than you.

506
00:38:37,130 --> 00:38:40,520
Are you ready to accept that?

507
00:38:41,430 --> 00:38:44,800
Also, not only will

508
00:38:44,800 --> 00:38:46,710
he treat work as his life,

509
00:38:46,710 --> 00:38:51,750
you also have to accept the complicated relationships around him.

510
00:38:54,260 --> 00:38:55,990
I can.

511
00:38:56,940 --> 00:38:58,890
Does he love you?

512
00:39:00,100 --> 00:39:02,250
Do you believe him?

513
00:39:02,250 --> 00:39:03,450
Yes.

514
00:39:03,450 --> 00:39:05,510
Okay. Since you've decided.

515
00:39:05,510 --> 00:39:07,250
Enjoy.

