00:39:36,580 --> 00:39:38,050
Qian Qian is back.

521
00:39:38,050 --> 00:39:41,380
Qian Qian is back? That's good news.

522
00:39:42,900 --> 00:39:45,550
But just then when you were on the phone, your attitude was...

523
00:39:45,550 --> 00:39:46,990
weird?

524
00:39:46,990 --> 00:39:49,180
