525
00:39:49,180 --> 00:39:51,400
What is it?

526
00:39:51,400 --> 00:39:53,050
Brain cancer.

527
00:39:54,250 --> 00:39:56,830
That's serious.

528
00:39:58,270 --> 00:40:01,430
