529
00:40:02,780 --> 00:40:04,820
I don't want to go.

530
00:40:04,820 --> 00:40:09,050
We have to be there together. She is very sick. How could you not go?

531
00:40:09,050 --> 00:40:12,430
It's not good for me to go. You go. You represent me.

532
00:40:12,430 --> 00:40:14,780
Why are you still saying things like this?

